<h3>演示如何访问 Local Datetime 字段</h3>

<p>点击按钮来创建 Local Datetime 字段。</p>

<button onclick="myFunction()">试一下</button>

<script>
function myFunction() {
    var x = document.createElement("INPUT");
    x.setAttribute("type", "datetime-local");
    document.body.appendChild(x);
}
</script>

</body>
